<a href="/api_resources">Platform API Reference</a> > <a href="/api_resources/30-apps">Apps</a> > List apps in an organization</div>
<p>
<h1>List apps in an organization</h1> 
</p>

<div class="row">
	<div class="span6" style="width:340px;">
		<p><b>API Platform Base Path:</b> https://api.enterprise.apigee.com/v1/o/{org_name}</p>
		<p><b>API Resource Path:</b> /apps</p>
		<p>
		Gets a list of app IDs in an organization
		</p>
	</div>

	<div class="span6" style="width:340px;">
		<p>
		<b>Verb:</b>
		<span class="verb-GET">GET</span>
		</p>
		<b>Auth:</b>
		Basic Auth
		</p>


	</div>
</div>

<div class="span18">
	<p>
	<p>Retrieves a list of all apps by ID within an organization.</p>
	</p>

	<b>Sample Request:</b>
	<pre>$ curl https://api.enterprise.apigee.com/v1/o/{org_name}/apps \
-u myname:mypass </pre>


<b>Sample Response:</b> 
	<pre>[ "7b3ec66d-de8b-4ab5-8025-d949285bed4f", "3cb6d175-0cb9-5521-bcbd-c9b33b64fffe"  ]</pre>


	

</div>




            </div>
